beforeBatch(int) - Method in interface bactimas.alg.ITrackingAlgorithm
Invoked before processing batch.
Eg, say a user wants to process 10 frames:
beforeBatch is called once before
beforeStep is called 10 times
Typically used to show a dialog and acquire algorithm parameters.
